的社交媒體並威脅到人生安全，在此籠罩著各種白色恐怖。面對這狀況每一位同路人更加要團結及爭取支持自由民主的政黨派系的支持及幫忙。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fprime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia%3Futm_content%3Dbandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%253Av12%26recruited_by_id%3Df7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612%26recruiter%3D889993192%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_petition&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=26cbf8e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition</a>"},{"pid":"4ab7682f8f6101bcc3e8e9998456d20a6940ec1b","tid":1540543,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"保護在澳香港學生please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地翻香港既人身安全已經係個Question Mark<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAlso 英藉港人 and Their 後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>Protect the pro-democracy Hongkongers in Australia</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889